contents.shortDescription: A casual yet elegant sofa that offers comfort and modern styling to accent your home's living room.
contents.name: Casual Sofa
contents.longDescription: Modernize your living room space with the casual sofa. The sofa features cool tones, removable seat pillows, easy to clean polyester fabric, and an additional accent pillow along the backrest. The armchair's modern styling is complemented with durable brushed steel legs along its corners and center, for extra support. No assembly required.

items.name: Braided Accent Rug
items.shortDescription: A stylish hand-crafted accent rug that features a pointed braided texture to accent your living space in a warm, welcoming way.
items.longDescription: Complete the look of your contemporary living room by adding a modern touch with this luxurious accent rug.  The rug is made of 100% wool, and contains a latex backing to prevent it from unwanted moving.

merchandisingAssociations.name: Abstract Glass Coffee Table

items.name: Abstract Glass Coffee Table
items.shortDescription: A modern styled coffee table that is suited towards open-concept areas, providing plenty of space for your refreshments and decor.
items.longDescription: Use this versatile glass coffee table's large round surface to display decor, and serve your guest's their coffee, tea, and desserts. Its table top features durable and easy-to-clean tempered glass, and its stylish clawed draw attention to the table top's contents.

merchandisingAssociations.shortDescription: A compact pub-style coffee table that provides modern styling and room for all types of refreshments.
merchandisingAssociations.name: Pub-style Coffee Table

items.name: Pub-style Coffee Table
items.shortDescription: A compact pub-style coffee table that provides modern styling and room for all types of refreshments.
items.longDescription: Perfect for after-dinner drinks in a cozy, intimate setting, this modern pub-style coffee table features a glass top that hovers above its wooden base to provide a bar-height coffee table. Its table top features durable and easy-to-clean tempered glass, and its stylish chrome legs keep it high off the ground for easy cleaning.

merchandisingAssociations.name: Weathered Pendant Light

items.name: Weathered Pendant Light
items.shortDescription: A rustic pendant light fixture that adds a vintage feel to any living space.
items.longDescription: Create that perfect feel and match your warm home decor by using this rustic pendant light. Use individually to project onto your decor, or use in sets based on your light coverage needs. Height adjustable.
